snippet.textDisplay: So many comments on every video on this channel always criticizing the owner of the car, saying they must be pigs or disgusting or ought to be ashamed. Nobody likes a filthy car! But it’s important to realize we don’t always know the circumstances of a person’s life. Someone could struggle to keep a clean car because they are disabled, because they are overwhelmed with other responsibilities, because of a hoarding disorder, all sorts of reasons! Yes the car is gross but to assume that justifies making such insensitive judgements about a person isn’t right.
